$ Service-level agreement
@ SLA

The SLA is an agreement between customers and service providers.

{ Aspects of service

  • Quality
  • Availability
  • Responsibility

}
{ Levels

  • Customer based SLAs
  • Service based SLAs
  • Multilevel SLAs

}
{ Common metrics

  • Abandonment rate
  • Average speed to answer (ASA)
  • Time service factor (TSF)
  • First call resolution (FCR)
  • Turn around time (TAT)
  • Mean time to recover (MTTR)

}
